WEBVTT

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:08.110
In the second bracket, #2, 
the most anticipated competitor...

00:00:08.110 --> 00:00:10.000
Tokai Teio!

00:00:12.510 --> 00:00:14.010
This feeling...

00:00:18.330 --> 00:00:20.030
Welcome back, Teio.

00:00:21.870 --> 00:00:22.700
Teio...

00:00:23.150 --> 00:00:25.900
If I race on her terms, 
I don't stand a chance.

00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:28.810
I need to run so that she's 
never able to catch up.

00:00:28.810 --> 00:00:30.650
Ikuno Dictus!

00:00:30.650 --> 00:00:34.320
Since your name's so long, can 
we just call cheer for "Ikuno"?

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:36.740
Wouldn't "Dictus" make more sense?

00:00:36.740 --> 00:00:38.500
Why don't we mix it up and go with Ikutus?

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:39.340
I like that!

00:00:39.340 --> 00:00:40.240
Ikutus!

00:00:40.240 --> 00:00:41.200
Ikutus!

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:42.450
I <i>do not care</i>.

00:00:48.420 --> 00:00:52.670
And McQueen shocks us all 
by coming in second place!

00:00:50.900 --> 00:00:51.900
{\an8}<font size="18" color="#5f68bc">Daitaku Helios</font>

00:00:52.880 --> 00:00:55.070
I was able to beat Mejiro McQueen.

00:00:55.070 --> 00:00:57.130
I can beat Tokai Teio, too!

00:00:57.130 --> 00:00:58.960
You better get psyched for this, Teio!

00:00:58.960 --> 00:00:59.380
Yeah!

00:00:59.380 --> 00:01:03.060
It's been about ten months. How's it feel 
to be on the turf again after so long?

00:01:03.060 --> 00:01:04.890
It feels really great!

00:01:04.890 --> 00:01:06.060
I can't wait to get started!

00:01:06.060 --> 00:01:08.300
I guess we don't need to worry, then.

00:01:08.810 --> 00:01:11.390
I'm gonna be running against 
McQueen in the Tennoushou,

00:01:11.390 --> 00:01:13.400
so I can't lose in a race like this!

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:17.240
Then, by all means, show me how you run, Teio.

00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:20.100
Yeah! I'm gonna head out, then!

