 She hasn't made her move yet!

00:03:22.490 --> 00:03:24.240
Tokai Teio is biding her time!

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:26.160
Forget about the 
runners in front of her!

00:03:28.500 --> 00:03:29.520
Okay.

00:03:34.300 --> 00:03:36.010
Tokai Teio!

00:03:36.010 --> 00:03:38.220
Here we go, ladies and gentlemen!

00:03:38.220 --> 00:03:40.170
Tokai Teio is moving up on the outside!

00:03:40.170 --> 00:03:43.180
She's entered her spurt down 
the final straightaway!

00:03:43.820 --> 00:03:45.680
My legs feel so light.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:47.300
Yeah, I can win this!

00:03:47.300 --> 00:03:49.310
Please, stop making this look so easy!

00:03:49.310 --> 00:03:52.270
And Tokai moves into the lead with ease!

00:03:52.270 --> 00:03:54.130
She's leaving all the others behind!

00:03:55.190 --> 00:03:57.190
Go!

00:03:58.180 --> 00:03:59.690
Is she...

00:03:59.690 --> 00:04:01.780
Tokai Teio is running uncontested!

00:04:01.780 --> 00:04:04.160
The Tennoushou is shaping up 
to be an incredible race!

00:04:04.160 --> 00:04:07.820
And Tokai Teio has cleared 
the goal like it was nothing!

00:04:07.820 --> 00:04:11.830
She's back! Tokai Teio has truly returned!

00:04:16.460 --> 00:04:19.630
Teio-san looked like she had 
plenty of effort to spare!

00:04:19.630 --> 00:04:20.980
She's not even a little tired!

00:04:20.980 --> 00:04:22.650
And she still dominated...

00:04:22.650 --> 00:04:23.720
That's totally nuts!

00:04:24.370 --> 00:04:25.530
What could be...

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:35.110
Excuse me, but isn't she faster 
than she was before her injury?

00:04:35.110 --> 00:04:38.230
Hosoe-san, this makes the Tennoushou 
that much more exciting, doesn't it?

00:04:38.230 --> 00:04:40.200
She'll be going up against Mejiro McQueen,

00:04:40.200 --> 00:04:41.980
who's got a ton of momentum right now.

00:04:48.010 --> 00:04:49.300
She's...

00:04:49.300 --> 00:04:51.080
On a totally different level!

00:04:51.080 --> 00:04:53.330
UMA SPORTS
THE LEGEND OF TEIO THE UNDEFEATED

00:04:51.420 --> 00:04:53.330
